fields.Ad_Description: I don't like math, so I'm getting rid of my math textbook. I hope someone else can get more enjoyment out of it than I can
I learned a lot from this book, but have learned all I can. It is time for someone else to find enjoyment from it
I learned so many cool design patterns from this book. I apply them in every single program I write. This is a must have book for anyone serious about learning Computer Science
Before I read this book, I had no idea how to code. Now, I'm a coding god who writes the cleanest code in the world.
This book caused me so much pain and suffering. Please take it from me!
Another one of my favourites. I'm sad to see it go, but there's simply not enough room on my book shelve.
This was a good read. I wish I could read it again, but I can't find the time.
Say what you will about Grimaldi, but I for one am a fan. I hope after buying this book from me, you'll be a fan too!
